  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.4">
<l>tēvu mepporu ḷumpa ṭaikkap</l>
<l>pūvi ṉāṉmuka ṉaippa ṭaitta</l>
<l>tēva ṉemperu māṉuk kallāl</l>
<l>pūvum pūca ṉaiyun takumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Other than for the god, our lord</l>
<l>who created the four-faced one in the flower</l>
<l>so that he would create the gods and all things,</l>
<l>are flowers and worship befitting?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
